a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527314\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527314\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eue1665702684659.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eue1665702684659.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eue1665702684659.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eue1665702684659\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $formtitle\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"eue1665702684659___formtitle_267407\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the title of the window title containing the Form instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"eue1665702684659__topic_d84053e1_d84054e1_d84055e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84056e1_d84057e1_d84058e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84059e1_d84060e1_d84061e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormTitle</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__section_w165ab1b7b5_w166ab1b7_w167ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84062e1_d84063e1_d84064e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$formtitle = \"Races\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eue1665702684659__topic_d55637e1_d55638e1_d55639e1_d55640e1_d55641e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722271e87\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormTitle</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"eue1665702684659__table_d8708e1_d8709e1_d8710e1__entry__3\">\n New title for the form. The maximum number of characters that can be assigned is 127.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eue1665702684659__topic_d55642e1_d55643e1_d55644e1_d55645e1_d55646e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722271e141\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84071e1_d84072e1_d84073e1\">Title of the current Form or Form instance.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84074e1_d84075e1_d84076e1\">Initially, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> returns the title of the Form as defined by the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Title</span> property, or the instance name, if no title has been set.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eue1665702684659__topic_d55647e1_d55648e1_d55649e1_d55650e1_d55651e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722271e160\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84080e1_d84081e1_d84082e1\">Use in Form components and Static Server Pages. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> is used in other components, it is ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eue1665702684659__topic_d55652e1_d55653e1_d55654e1_d55655e1_d55656e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722271e172\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84086e1_d84087e1_d84088e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> to dynamically set the title of the form window.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eue1665702684659__p_d84089e1_d84090e1_d84091e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> function has effect only when an application is using a GUI driver. Changing <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> overrides the value defined in the GUI-specific settings.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eue1665702684659__section_db2_111_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d722271e193\">Example: Naming Forms </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span> to name the\n               form window after the race season the user is accessing:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"eue1665702684659__pre_cn4_111_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; FORMULA 1 Application\n; form: W_RACE\noperation exec\n$valrep(RACE_DLIST.RACE) = $$list\n$formtitle = \"Races - %%$$season season\"\ncall lp_clearvars\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527314\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527314\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$formtitle Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $formtitle Return or set the title of the window title containing the Form instance. $formtitle $formtitle = FormTitle Example: $formtitle = \"Races\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description FormTitle String New title for the form. The maximum number of characters that can be assigned is 127. Return Values Title of the current Form or Form instance. Initially, $formtitle returns the title of the Form as defined by the Title property, or the instance name, if no title has been set. Use Use in Form components and Static Server Pages. If $formtitle is used in other components, it is ignored. Description You can use $formtitle to dynamically set the title of the form window. The $formtitle function has effect only when an application is using a GUI driver. Changing $formtitle overrides the value defined in the GUI-specific settings. Example: Naming Forms The following example uses $formtitle to name the form window after the race season the user is accessing: ; FORMULA 1 Application ; form: W_RACE operation exec $valrep(RACE_DLIST.RACE) = $$list $formtitle = \"Races - %%$$season season\" call lp_clearvars edit end; exec Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}